Pandemonium everywhere.

02:22.881 --> 02:25.971
You can not the authorities.

02:26.102 --> 02:26.972
You couldn't even get through.

02:31.412 --> 02:33.065
With all these
energy surges, it's

02:33.196 --> 02:36.982
been difficult to keep track ofeveryone and locate everyone.

02:37.113 --> 02:40.638
Uh, and some people
are still missing.

02:45.469 --> 02:49.430
There are rumors that
maybe it's biblical.

02:49.560 --> 02:57.351
But as a scientist,
um, I just don't know.

02:57.481 --> 02:57.960
Not yet.

03:01.877 --> 03:05.141
Not yet.

