07:34.889 --> 07:36.760
Hey.

07:36.891 --> 07:38.196
Hey, honey?

07:38.327 --> 07:39.720
You OK?

07:39.850 --> 07:42.418
Yeah, she's all rightnow, aren't you, sweetie?

07:44.028 --> 07:44.507
Adam!

07:44.638 --> 07:45.247
Look out!

