08:43.174 --> 08:44.698
Fuck, damn it.

08:46.047 --> 08:47.614
Um, a door.

08:47.744 --> 08:49.790
Um, uh, what kind of door?

08:54.795 --> 08:57.711
Can you describe the sound?

08:57.841 --> 08:59.190
