09:33.660 --> 09:35.139
KATHY: Hello.

09:35.270 --> 09:36.532
Fucking bugged out in themiddle of the apocalypse.

09:36.663 --> 09:37.228
Right here.

09:37.359 --> 09:38.229
See.

