09:54.985 --> 09:56.073
Yeah, they're all--we're not supposed to print

09:56.204 --> 09:58.685
transcripts without an order.

09:58.815 --> 10:00.730
If she's not there, why
do you think she's dead?

10:00.861 --> 10:01.862
Right here.

10:01.992 --> 10:03.559
Kathy, they called us--

10:03.690 --> 10:05.648
they tried to contact us
because they wanted us--

10:05.779 --> 10:06.867
Stop!

10:06.997 --> 10:08.695
Stop!

10:08.825 --> 10:10.087
The only reason you're
still working here

10:10.218 --> 10:11.741
is because I let this
crazy shit slide.

10:11.872 --> 10:14.135
But right now, you are
my last fucking nerve,

10:14.265 --> 10:16.528
and you need to sit your
nutty ass down and go

10:16.659 --> 10:17.965
and answer some goddamn calls.

10:18.095 --> 10:18.618
Now!

10:37.375 --> 10:39.682
DISPATCHER: 9-1-1,
what's your emergency?

10:39.813 --> 10:41.162
What is your name and location?

10:46.776 --> 10:49.910
9-1-1, what's your emergency?

11:00.137 --> 11:02.183
