11:20.636 --> 11:21.332
Keep people safe.

11:40.438 --> 11:43.267
OK, listen up everyone.

11:43.398 --> 11:45.661
Homeland Security isreporting a major incident

11:45.792 --> 11:47.968
with one of these things.

11:48.098 --> 11:49.273
Homeland Security?

11:49.404 --> 11:50.971
Emergency services
are responding.

11:51.101 --> 11:52.233
What are we supposed
to tell people?

